Dialogue: 2,0:00:11.28,0:00:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...Takasu-san had agreed to produce the same song for Wakamatsu Madoka.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:15.57,0:00:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Then... who should we ask to be Full Moon's Producer?
Dialogue: 2,0:00:20.34,0:00:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Well, then...
Dialogue: 2,0:00:21.07,0:00:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...I wonder what's going to happen today.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:22.90,0:00:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:00:27.64,0:00:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1\pos(320,460)}Do you understand?
Dialogue: 2,0:00:29.10,0:00:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1\pos(320,460)}Yes.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:31.34,0:00:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\an8}Paging Dr. Nakamura.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:33.38,0:00:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\an8}Please contact the front desk immediately.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:35.55,0:00:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\an8}Paging Dr. Nakamura.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:37.55,0:00:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\an8}Please contact the front desk immediately...
Dialogue: 2,0:00:38.72,0:00:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Come on.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:39.89,0:00:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}O-Okay...
Dialogue: 2,0:00:42.77,0:00:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 2,0:00:44.27,0:00:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Aren't you going to knock?
Dialogue: 2,0:00:47.92,0:00:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:00:48.82,0:00:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What's up, Mitsuki-chan?
Dialogue: 2,0:00:49.90,0:00:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Why are you here?
Dialogue: 2,0:00:52.65,0:00:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:53.44,0:00:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Um... that's...
Dialogue: 2,0:00:54.82,0:00:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I just happened to be in the area...
Dialogue: 2,0:00:56.91,0:00:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}B-Bye.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:08.04,0:01:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\fscx90\fscy90\be1}I see...
Dialogue: 2,0:01:09.21,0:01:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\fscx90\fscy90\be1}It's not an easy thing to ask for, huh...
Dialogue: 2,0:01:11.11,0:01:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\fscx90\fscy90\be1}I'll talk to him myself then.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:13.17,0:01:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\fscx90\fscy90\be1}Mitsuki, you just wait there.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:14.72,0:01:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Okay...
Dialogue: 2,0:01:15.47,0:01:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Sorry...
Dialogue: 2,0:01:20.39,0:01:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hey, I'm the one who should be sighing.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:23.27,0:01:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Why didn't you just ask him?
Dialogue: 2,0:01:25.35,0:01:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's 'cause...
Dialogue: 2,0:01:26.56,0:01:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What am I supposed to say...?
Dialogue: 2,0:01:28.40,0:01:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's like a little kid playing make-believe...
Dialogue: 2,0:01:29.98,0:01:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I feel like I'm dragging Wakaouji-sensei into this...
Dialogue: 2,0:01:33.32,0:01:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}We're not playing make-believe here!
Dialogue: 2,0:01:35.53,0:01:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Man, you worry way too much!
Dialogue: 2,0:01:38.16,0:01:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Anyways, you know...
Dialogue: 2,0:01:39.32,0:01:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's not acting child-like.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:40.95,0:01:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Y-You think?
Dialogue: 2,0:01:42.74,0:01:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's not child-like, is it...?
Dialogue: 2,0:01:45.50,0:01:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}And what's with that Takuto...
Dialogue: 2,0:01:47.75,0:01:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}He's the one who said that we should all go \Ntogether, and then he's like...
Dialogue: 2,0:01:49.88,0:01:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}"It be better if I didn't".
Dialogue: 2,0:01:51.54,0:01:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What's he trying to do?!
Dialogue: 2,0:01:52.88,0:01:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah...
Dialogue: 2,0:01:53.76,0:01:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}When Takuto said that he shouldn't, he wasn't lying.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:56.59,0:01:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 2,0:01:57.63,0:01:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Wakaouji-sensei, that is...
Dialogue: 2,0:01:59.76,0:02:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I guess he doesn't really like him...
Dialogue: 2,0:02:02.60,0:02:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Why's that?
Dialogue: 2,0:02:08.39,0:02:15.11,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I want Wakaouji-sensei and Takuto to get along, but I guess it's impossible.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:15.11,0:02:17.61,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}A doctor... and a Shinigami...
Dialogue: 2,0:02:37.38,0:02:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}So... if we have a former member of Route L as the producer,
Dialogue: 2,0:02:41.51,0:02:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}then we can use that to target old fans of Route L and draw them in as well.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:49.56,0:02:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It'd be something like this.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:51.73,0:02:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Wow...
Dialogue: 2,0:02:52.77,0:02:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's like grown-ups doing business...
Dialogue: 2,0:02:59.36,0:03:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I refuse.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:00.49,0:03:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:03:02.66,0:03:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}C-Can you tell me why?
Dialogue: 2,0:03:05.41,0:03:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah...
Dialogue: 2,0:03:06.16,0:03:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'll tell you the truth.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:07.66,0:03:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}If you don't produce it, then this plan won't be possible.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:12.54,0:03:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}For Mitsuki's sake...
Dialogue: 2,0:03:14.34,0:03:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...can you please do this?
Dialogue: 2,0:03:17.71,0:03:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I refuse.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:19.01,0:03:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Why?!
Dialogue: 2,0:03:20.51,0:03:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}My reason doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:22.01,0:03:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}No way...
Dialogue: 2,0:03:22.43,0:03:23.93,Overlap,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's right...
Dialogue: 2,0:03:23.93,0:03:25.26,Overlap,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's no use...
Dialogue: 2,0:03:25.95,0:03:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}They're really going at it now...
Dialogue: 2,0:03:25.26,0:03:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You're the only one I can ask Dr. Wakaouji!
Dialogue: 2,0:03:27.31,0:03:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You should understand how hard it is!
Dialogue: 2,0:04:18.61,0:04:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}This will be the conceptual image that we're going to use.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:21.07,0:04:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Q-Quite untraditional...
Dialogue: 2,0:04:23.07,0:04:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}But, it seems like a mismatch...
Dialogue: 2,0:04:26.16,0:04:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You hit it right on the nose.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:27.45,0:04:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Is is a mismatch.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:28.62,0:04:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:04:29.74,0:04:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}On top of the appeal that her raw, primitive feel has,
Dialogue: 2,0:04:33.25,0:04:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'll throw in something completely different to complement it.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:36.58,0:04:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Understand?
Dialogue: 2,0:04:37.38,0:04:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 2,0:04:39.75,0:04:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Which means that I want each of you to keep this conceptual image in mind.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:43.72,0:04:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Any questions?
Dialogue: 2,0:04:48.18,0:04:49.93,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Takasu Kouhei...
Dialogue: 2,0:04:49.93,0:04:53.43,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}He's not known as the Hit-Maker for nothing...
Dialogue: 2,0:04:53.43,0:04:55.06,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}He'll make me...
Dialogue: 2,0:04:55.06,0:04:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\i1}Hey! Look here please!
Dialogue: 2,0:04:55.77,0:04:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\i1}Madoka-chan, over here!
Dialogue: 2,0:04:57.36,0:04:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\i1}Okay!
Dialogue: 2,0:05:01.48,0:05:03.57,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...into a top star!
Dialogue: 2,0:05:12.75,0:05:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Sorry...
Dialogue: 2,0:05:13.96,0:05:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I guess the plan was flawed.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:16.12,0:05:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}We'll have to patch things up.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:17.83,0:05:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}But... how do we do that...
Dialogue: 2,0:05:22.38,0:05:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Um...
Dialogue: 2,0:05:23.34,0:05:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ooshige-san...
Dialogue: 2,0:05:24.55,0:05:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It might be a problem for him.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:26.18,0:05:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hey. Don't say that.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:28.34,0:05:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's your song.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:30.01,0:05:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yeah...
Dialogue: 2,0:05:30.97,0:05:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hey... Mitsuki...
