Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.63,0:07:34.93,Note,,0,0,0,Note,{\be1\fad(200,200)}[Amidakuji: Ladder lottery (used to make decisions, choose turns, or assign prizes)]
Dialogue: 2,0:07:30.63,0:07:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Amidakuji, I guess...
Dialogue: 2,0:07:35.85,0:07:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Again?
Dialogue: 2,0:07:41.31,0:07:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah!
Dialogue: 2,0:07:42.19,0:07:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 2,0:07:43.65,0:07:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It'll be the same no matter how many times you keep doing it.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:45.48,0:07:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}No matter which one comes up, \Nyou'll never be satisfied, will you?
Dialogue: 2,0:07:48.42,0:07:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Besides, what are you thinking, using amidakuji to decide this...
Dialogue: 2,0:07:54.16,0:07:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You're right...
Dialogue: 2,0:07:56.03,0:07:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That doctor...
Dialogue: 2,0:07:57.20,0:07:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm sure he could tell...
Dialogue: 2,0:07:58.70,0:08:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...that you aren't sure about how you feel yet.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:01.16,0:08:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I get it.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:02.92,0:08:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}So that's why he said no, huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:08:04.88,0:08:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Be clear about your own feelings first.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:07.46,0:08:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I agree!
Dialogue: 2,0:08:10.17,0:08:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You know, I...
Dialogue: 2,0:08:12.59,0:08:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...I could never give up on music...
Dialogue: 2,0:08:15.68,0:08:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}But Wakaouji-sensei gave it up for good...
Dialogue: 2,0:08:20.14,0:08:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...even though he loved music.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:23.77,0:08:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It must have been a hard thing to do.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:27.36,0:08:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Much harder than what I'm going through...
Dialogue: 2,0:08:30.36,0:08:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Maybe.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:31.82,0:08:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}But, just because of that...
Dialogue: 2,0:08:33.28,0:08:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...you're not going to say that you're giving up {\i1}Eternal Snow{\i0}, right?
Dialogue: 2,0:08:36.95,0:08:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Well...
Dialogue: 2,0:08:38.24,0:08:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I won't give up on it.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:40.20,0:08:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Is that so...
Dialogue: 2,0:08:41.83,0:08:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Then... everything's okay.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:49.88,0:08:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What do we have to do next?
Dialogue: 2,0:08:51.63,0:08:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}We're studying the movement of the constellations and the Moon.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:56.26,0:08:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh?!
Dialogue: 2,0:08:57.09,0:08:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You got your own computer?!
Dialogue: 2,0:08:59.12,0:09:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yep!
Dialogue: 2,0:09:00.06,0:09:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Must be nice...
Dialogue: 2,0:09:01.39,0:09:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}My daddy's so kind.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:03.27,0:09:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}He'll do anything I ask!
Dialogue: 2,0:09:06.15,0:09:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Kind? More like he's spoiling you...
Dialogue: 2,0:09:09.57,0:09:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You're so mean!
Dialogue: 2,0:09:14.07,0:09:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\i1}Wakaouji-sensei!{\i0}
Dialogue: 2,0:09:15.70,0:09:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\i1}I have a favor to ask!{\i0} {}
Dialogue: 2,0:09:18.99,0:09:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\i1}Please be my producer!{\i0}
Dialogue: 2,0:09:20.79,0:09:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\i1}If Mitsuki-chan's asking me, \NI can't very well refuse.{\i0}
Dialogue: 2,0:09:23.91,0:09:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\i1}Yay!{\i0}
Dialogue: 2,0:09:24.83,0:09:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\i1}I'm so happy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 2,0:09:26.33,0:09:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\i1}I love you, Wakaouji-sensei!{\i0}
Dialogue: 2,0:09:30.75,0:09:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That kind of conversation could never happen...
Dialogue: 2,0:09:36.05,0:09:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}We want to do {\i1}Eternal Snow{\i0}... no matter what!
Dialogue: 2,0:09:38.39,0:09:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Why are you so determined on doing that?
Dialogue: 2,0:09:40.60,0:09:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Because... you're telling us to change the song, boss!
Dialogue: 2,0:09:42.85,0:09:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}In reality, that won't work.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:44.18,0:09:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You can't do {\i1}Eternal Snow.{\i0}
Dialogue: 2,0:09:46.48,0:09:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You haven't even found anyone who's willing to produce it.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:49.06,0:09:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm currently talking it over with someone.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:51.32,0:09:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}And you think that Seed Records will be okay with that person...?
Dialogue: 2,0:09:54.65,0:09:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I believe that they will be!
Dialogue: 2,0:09:56.90,0:09:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I didn't want to say this, but...
Dialogue: 2,0:09:58.41,0:10:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...if you keep this up, I'll have to transfer you.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:00.62,0:10:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Transfer?
Dialogue: 2,0:10:02.20,0:10:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You mean... change managers?
Dialogue: 2,0:10:04.62,0:10:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}To put it bluntly, that's correct.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:07.08,0:10:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}T-That's...
Dialogue: 2,0:10:33.11,0:10:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}This is Cassiopeia at seven o'clock.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:36.61,0:10:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Here... two hours later, at nine o'clock...
Dialogue: 2,0:10:39.99,0:10:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It shape has stayed the same,\Nbut its position has changed like so.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:44.58,0:10:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yes.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:45.16,0:10:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Excellent job.'
Dialogue: 2,0:10:46.04,0:10:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Return to your seat.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:50.46,0:10:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 2,0:10:51.42,0:10:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You don't look to happy.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:53.71,0:10:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's nothing, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:56.63,0:11:00.84,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}This is the one thing that I can't talk to Tomoe-chan about...
Dialogue: 2,0:11:01.34,0:11:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}As Maijima explained...
Dialogue: 2,0:11:03.26,0:11:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...the shape of the constellation does not change as time passes...
Dialogue: 2,0:11:06.31,0:11:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}However, the position in the sky {\i1}do {\i0} change.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:10.06,0:11:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Then, next...
Dialogue: 2,0:11:11.23,0:11:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...let's look at the relationship between the Earth and the Moon.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:15.15,0:11:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}The Moon as everyone knows...
Dialogue: 2,0:11:16.82,0:11:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...doesn't shine by itself.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:18.78,0:11:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:11:19.49,0:11:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Do you know what makes it shine, then?
Dialogue: 2,0:11:21.91,0:11:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hasegawa, do you know?
Dialogue: 2,0:11:23.98,0:11:25.24,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hey Mitsuki.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:25.24,0:11:26.45,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}The Moon...
Dialogue: 2,0:11:26.45,0:11:29.21,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It doesn't shine on its own.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:29.21,0:11:29.91,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Then...
Dialogue: 2,0:11:29.91,0:11:31.67,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}How does it shine?
Dialogue: 2,0:11:31.67,0:11:32.88,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's because...
Dialogue: 2,0:11:33.67,0:11:35.67,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}With the Sun at the center...
Dialogue: 2,0:11:35.67,0:11:38.42,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...the Earth and the Moon revolve around it.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:39.97,0:11:44.85,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Because it reflects the light from the sun like a mirror...
Dialogue: 2,0:11:44.85,0:11:47.72,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Then, if there was no Sun...
Dialogue: 2,0:11:47.72,0:11:49.23,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...the moon wouldn't shine?
Dialogue: 2,0:11:49.23,0:11:50.35,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's right.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:50.89,0:11:51.64,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That means...
Dialogue: 2,0:11:52.19,0:11:53.10,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That means?
Dialogue: 2,0:11:53.60,0:11:56.11,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eichi-kun is my Sun!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:57.40,0:11:58.98,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}But I'm not the only one...
Dialogue: 2,0:11:58.98,0:11:59.65,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:11:59.99,0:12:01.53,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}The teachers at the orphanage...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:01.53,0:12:02.86,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}The teachers at school...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:02.86,0:12:03.78,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Your friends...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:03.78,0:12:04.82,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}And...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:05.24,0:12:07.74,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Your father and mother, who have passed on...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:09.29,0:12:12.00,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}They're all helping you sing, aren't they?
Dialogue: 2,0:12:12.96,0:12:13.67,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:13.67,0:12:16.29,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}So... just be yourself...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:16.29,0:12:18.46,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Stay true to yourself.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:18.96,0:12:21.38,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Everyone is helping you shine.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:22.38,0:12:23.63,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eichi-kun...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:23.63,0:12:24.93,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:28.93,0:12:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'll go try and ask him!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:34.48,0:12:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}M-Mitsuki?
Dialogue: 2,0:12:37.19,0:12:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Can the teacher ask for something too?
Dialogue: 2,0:12:40.48,0:12:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Please, I'd like you to sit down.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:45.78,0:12:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Kouyama-san did it again!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:53.16,0:12:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}So, what did you need?
Dialogue: 2,0:12:55.37,0:12:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Wakaouji-sensei, I'm begging you.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:58.00,0:13:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Please accept the position as my producer!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:02.01,0:13:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}So that's what this is about.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:03.72,0:13:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You know, even if it's Mitsuki-chan who's asking me...
Dialogue: 2,0:13:06.97,0:13:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...there's some things that I can do, and some things that I just can't.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:09.35,0:13:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I understand what you mean, but I still have to ask you...
Dialogue: 2,0:13:14.27,0:13:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Wakaouji-sensei...
Dialogue: 2,0:13:15.94,0:13:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...I want you to help me do {\i1}Eternal Snow{\i0} !
Dialogue: 2,0:13:20.19,0:13:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's impossible, Mitsuki-chan.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:22.99,0:13:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm happy you feel that way, though...
Dialogue: 2,0:13:24.78,0:13:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I see...
Dialogue: 2,0:13:27.07,0:13:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Doesn't he have any regrets?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:28.45,0:13:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:29.24,0:13:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What did you just say?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:30.78,0:13:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I said, doesn't he have any regrets?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:33.08,0:13:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}W-What do you mean?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:34.75,0:13:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Mitsuki-chan, who are you...
Dialogue: 2,0:13:37.17,0:13:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Could it be those two...
Dialogue: 2,0:13:40.92,0:13:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}She won't ask you, so I'm going to do it myself.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:44.05,0:13:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:44.92,0:13:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}So you really don't feel anything for music now?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:48.59,0:13:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Nothing at all.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:49.93,0:13:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm so envious...
Dialogue: 2,0:13:52.39,0:13:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:53.77,0:13:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Well, I'm a Shinigami...
Dialogue: 2,0:13:56.64,0:13:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I see all kinds of people in my line of work
Dialogue: 2,0:13:59.44,0:14:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Every one of them... dies with regrets...
Dialogue: 2,0:14:02.32,0:14:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}If only I had done that...
Dialogue: 2,0:14:03.98,0:14:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}If only I had done this...
Dialogue: 2,0:14:06.26,0:14:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}S-Stop it Takuto!
Dialogue: 2,0:14:08.32,0:14:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}This isn't something I should be saying, but...
Dialogue: 2,0:14:09.87,0:14:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...while you're still alive is the only time when you can do what you love. {edited}
Dialogue: 2,0:14:14.08,0:14:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That means that you have to give it your all!
Dialogue: 2,0:14:17.75,0:14:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I don't want to hear that from a Shinigami.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:20.71,0:14:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I suppose so.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:22.21,0:14:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}On top of that, I look like a stuffed animal.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:25.26,0:14:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm probably not convincing at all.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:27.55,0:14:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}But, you know...
Dialogue: 2,0:14:29.26,0:14:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...it's just like I said.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:30.55,0:14:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You can only do what you love while you're alive.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:33.31,0:14:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's why she's working so hard.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:35.60,0:14:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}While what little is left of her life...
Dialogue: 2,0:14:37.52,0:14:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}With that tiny body of hers...
Dialogue: 2,0:14:39.56,0:14:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}There will be suffering... there will be sadness...
Dialogue: 2,0:14:42.90,0:14:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}But, if she can sing a song that she loves...
Dialogue: 2,0:14:47.36,0:14:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I-I'm sorry, Wakaouji-sensei!
Dialogue: 2,0:14:49.95,0:14:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Sorry to be a bother to you. {edited}
Dialogue: 2,0:14:51.99,0:14:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Excuse us!
Dialogue: 2,0:14:58.50,0:15:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hey, you damn brat!
Dialogue: 2,0:15:05.80,0:15:07.17,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Back then...
Dialogue: 2,0:15:07.17,0:15:10.27,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...when Route L decided to split...
Dialogue: 2,0:15:10.27,0:15:12.18,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...I tossed music.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:13.97,0:15:16.06,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}In a world that had nothing to do with music...
Dialogue: 2,0:15:16.06,0:15:18.27,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...I thought that I could live a different life.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:20.31,0:15:22.15,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I chose the path of a doctor.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:22.65,0:15:24.86,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I have never regretted it.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:25.44,0:15:27.44,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}A doctor is a worthwhile job.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:27.86,0:15:28.86,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}But...
Dialogue: 2,0:15:36.16,0:15:38.79,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...every time I heard music, it hurt inside...
Dialogue: 2,0:15:39.41,0:15:41.33,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Like reopening an old wound...
Dialogue: 2,0:15:41.71,0:15:44.33,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I wonder... if that was regret...
Dialogue: 2,0:15:44.33,0:15:46.17,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}If it was, I...
Dialogue: 2,0:15:49.09,0:15:51.81,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Compared to that, Mitsuki-chan is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.81,0:15:59.23,Myself Romaji ED2 (Commented),,0,0,0,Song,Doushite konna ni suki nandarou
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.81,0:15:59.23,Myself TL(Pre-Credits),,0,0,0,Song,Why do I love you so?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.23,0:16:06.39,Myself Romaji ED2 (Commented),,0,0,0,Song,Kimi no koe kanashii hodo hibiiteru yo
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.23,0:16:06.39,Myself TL(Pre-Credits),,0,0,0,Song,Your voice is calling out with such sadness...
Dialogue: 2,0:16:10.40,0:16:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Only while you're still alive, huh...
Dialogue: 2,0:16:13.95,0:16:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Geez!
Dialogue: 2,0:16:14.66,0:16:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Geez! Stupid Takuto!
Dialogue: 2,0:16:16.83,0:16:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Why'd you say all those things to Wakaouji-sensei!
Dialogue: 2,0:16:20.20,0:16:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hey! I couldn't just stand there any longer!
Dialogue: 2,0:16:26.08,0:16:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hey, hey...
Dialogue: 2,0:16:27.46,0:16:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Did something happen?
Dialogue: 2,0:16:28.67,0:16:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}The hell if I know!
Dialogue: 2,0:16:29.67,0:16:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That blockhead...
Dialogue: 2,0:16:30.76,0:16:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Oh...
Dialogue: 2,0:16:31.63,0:16:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}So you're going to let me be the odd one out?
Dialogue: 2,0:16:34.36,0:16:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Fine!
Dialogue: 2,0:16:41.93,0:16:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Late...
Dialogue: 2,0:16:43.48,0:16:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yeah...
Dialogue: 2,0:16:44.31,0:16:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I wonder what's wrong.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:46.33,0:16:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Mitsuki...
Dialogue: 2,0:16:48.36,0:16:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ooshige-san!
Dialogue: 2,0:16:50.53,0:16:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Sorry... I'm late...
Dialogue: 2,0:16:53.32,0:16:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What's wrong? You look awful...
Dialogue: 2,0:16:57.03,0:16:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I drank too much last night.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:58.53,0:16:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Broken heart?
Dialogue: 2,0:16:59.54,0:17:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}No, I was just pissed off...
Dialogue: 2,0:17:01.33,0:17:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}About what?
Dialogue: 2,0:17:02.16,0:17:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}My boss...
Dialogue: 2,0:17:04.12,0:17:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Wait, that doesn't have anything to do with you!
Dialogue: 2,0:17:07.13,0:17:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Come on, let's go to work.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:11.59,0:17:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ooshige-san...
Dialogue: 2,0:17:12.59,0:17:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's dangerous...
Dialogue: 2,0:17:24.89,0:17:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Okay, good job!
Dialogue: 2,0:17:26.23,0:17:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:27.85,0:17:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Good work.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:28.06,0:17:28.69,Overlap,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hey!
Dialogue: 2,0:17:28.69,0:17:29.73,Overlap,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's over.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:31.82,0:17:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Is your headache any better?
Dialogue: 2,0:17:34.74,0:17:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}A little, I guess...
Dialogue: 2,0:17:37.03,0:17:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Wa-Wakaouji-sensei!
Dialogue: 2,0:17:42.37,0:17:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}The offer that you made a few days ago...
Dialogue: 2,0:17:44.12,0:17:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I spent some time thinking over it carefully.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:46.58,0:17:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Sensei, I'm very sorry about that!
Dialogue: 2,0:17:48.50,0:17:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}We won't bother you...
Dialogue: 2,0:17:48.50,0:17:49.59,Overlap,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}There are some conditions, but...
Dialogue: 2,0:17:50.63,0:17:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...I'll accept the position as Mitsuki's producer.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:55.72,0:17:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}C-Conditions?!
Dialogue: 2,0:17:57.05,0:17:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}If you want something...
Dialogue: 2,0:17:58.97,0:18:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I don't care about money.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:01.22,0:18:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'll get to make music again after all.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:06.39,0:18:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Then...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:07.23,0:18:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Then... what are the conditions?
Dialogue: 2,0:18:09.65,0:18:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}If it's something that we can do...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:12.27,0:18:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}My conditions are...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:14.65,0:18:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Mitsuki-chan...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:15.65,0:18:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah, yes...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:17.11,0:18:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}First...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:18.20,0:18:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...you have to get your throat checked regularly.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:20.99,0:18:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Second...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:22.08,0:18:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...when the time comes, promise to listen to what I said before
Dialogue: 2,0:18:24.87,0:18:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}We'll do the surgery, 'kay?
Dialogue: 2,0:18:26.83,0:18:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}S-Surgery?
Dialogue: 2,0:18:29.17,0:18:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:30.50,0:18:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Of course, I'll be the one doing the operation.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:33.80,0:18:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'll have to stop working full-time...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:35.05,0:18:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...and work part-time instead, though.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:36.76,0:18:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:18:39.55,0:18:41.60,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}A-Are you sure, Wakaouji-kun?
Dialogue: 2,0:18:41.60,0:18:44.18,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You've already been selected to serve as the next director...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:44.18,0:18:46.06,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'd like a little more time.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:46.60,0:18:48.27,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}This may be selfish of me to ask for, but...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:48.69,0:18:50.15,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...I'd like you to reconsider.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:51.56,0:18:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Sensei...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:53.36,0:18:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I have my own reasons as well.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:56.19,0:18:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I really can't forget about music.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:58.90,0:19:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}To tell you the truth, I actually wanted to resign...
Dialogue: 2,0:19:01.95,0:19:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}But there's something besides \Nmusic that I must do, after all.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:08.33,0:19:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That is... to heal Mitsuki-chan's throat.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:11.00,0:19:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Sensei...
Dialogue: 2,0:19:12.88,0:19:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I want to hear Mitsuki-chan sing {\i1}Eternal Snow {\i0} as well.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:17.76,0:19:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Your father in heaven...
Dialogue: 2,0:19:20.22,0:19:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}and your mother...
Dialogue: 2,0:19:21.47,0:19:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I want to let them hear it!
Dialogue: 2,0:19:23.43,0:19:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I...
Dialogue: 2,0:19:24.85,0:19:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...believe in you, Wakaouji-sensei.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:27.14,0:19:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}With your help, I'll be able to shine even more than before.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:30.85,0:19:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's what I plan to do.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:32.56,0:19:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm going to help you shine more and more...
Dialogue: 2,0:19:34.82,0:19:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...until Eichi-kun notices you.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:36.90,0:19:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Okay!
Dialogue: 2,0:19:39.19,0:19:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Also...
Dialogue: 2,0:19:40.36,0:19:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Here.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:42.53,0:19:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You dropped it in your room at the hospital.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:44.20,0:19:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I asked around, but no one knew what it was.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:46.99,0:19:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I figured it was probably yours.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:50.83,0:19:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Thank you, Wakaouji-sensei.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:53.04,0:19:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,435)\be1}I'm counting on you!
Dialogue: 2,0:19:55.54,0:19:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,435)\be1}So am I, Mitsuki-chan.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:58.26,0:20:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,435)\be1}No... {\i1}Full Moon.{\i0}
Dialogue: 2,0:20:00.05,0:20:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,435)\be1}Okay!
Dialogue: 2,0:21:36.27,0:21:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What are you fretting over, Meroko?
Dialogue: 2,0:21:38.31,0:21:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's great that we asked Wakaouji-sensei to be the producer for her new song, but...
Dialogue: 2,0:21:42.53,0:21:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...he won't let her sing at all!
Dialogue: 2,0:21:45.20,0:21:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}And then, he asks Mitsuki questions like "What do you want to tell people through your song?"
Dialogue: 2,0:21:49.66,0:21:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}At this rate, we'll never get it recorded.
Dialogue: 2,0:21:52.20,0:21:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's fine.
Dialogue: 2,0:21:52.99,0:21:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}She'll definitely find an answer!
Dialogue: 2,0:21:56.00,0:21:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Next time on Full Moon wo Sagashite:
Dialogue: 2,0:21:58.33,0:22:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What I Want to Say...
Dialogue: 2,0:22:00.03,0:22:01.42,Sync,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Look forward to it!
