Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.71,0:19:58.88,Myself ED2 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(200,100)}Why... just why have I fallen in love with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.88,0:20:05.35,Myself ED2 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\be3\fad(200,200)}Yet, still... I can't stop my tears from falling...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.44,0:20:24.70,Myself ED2 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(166,100)}I lost way too much back then
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.03,0:20:28.91,Myself ED2 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(210,0)}I couldn't sing at all
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.45,0:20:33.46,Myself ED2 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(250,100)}That place you had to leave for a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.46,0:20:40.96,Myself ED2 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(200,0)}It happened to be the place where I was
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.80,0:20:47.43,Myself ED2 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(210,100)}On that day I could see...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.14,0:20:52.18,Myself ED2 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(200,0)}The desolation lying in your eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.14,0:20:57.81,Myself ED2 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(210,0)}I wonder if it's the same for both of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.98,0:21:05.20,Myself ED2 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(250,0)}If you would just notice, I'm always by your side
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.66,0:21:11.29,Myself ED2 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(160,0)}Why do I love you so?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.50,0:21:17.29,Myself ED2 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(160,0)}Your voice is calling out with such sadness
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.58,0:21:23.34,Myself ED2 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(210,0)}I never knew what was supporting me, back then, and even now
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.01,0:21:31.43,Myself ED2 TL,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(210,840)}Until we became so far apart...
